title: TSError: тип Unable to compile TypeScript
body:
I did 'npx hardhat compile' and then on the generated typescript while i tried deploying the contract with 'npx hardhat run typechain/PanaromaswapV3Factory.d.ts --network ropsten', facing the issue with tserror.'Types of property 'functions' are incompatible.'

```
(base) debo@debo-ROG-Zephyrus-G14-GA401QE-GA401QE:~/bangfinals/v3-core$ npx hardhat run typechain/PanaromaswapV3Factory.d.ts --network ropsten --show-stack-traces
(node:7769) ExperimentalWarning: stream/web is an experimental feature. This feature could change at any time
(Use `node --trace-warnings ...` to show where the warning was created)
Creating Typechain artifacts in directory typechain for target ethers-v5
Successfully generated Typechain artifacts!

/home/debo/bangfinals/v3-core/node_modules/ts-node/src/index.ts:434
    return new TSError(diagnosticText, diagnosticCodes)
           ^
TSError: тип Unable to compile TypeScript:
typechain/PanaromaswapV3Factory.d.ts:23:11 - error TS2430: Interface 'PanaromaswapV3FactoryInterface' incorrectly extends interface 'Interface'.
  Types of property 'functions' are incompatible.
    Type '{ "createPool(address,address,uint24)": FunctionFragment; "enableFeeAmount(uint24,int24)": FunctionFragment; "feeAmountTickSpacing(uint24)": FunctionFragment; "getPool(address,address,uint24)": FunctionFragment; "owner()": FunctionFragment; "parameters()": FunctionFragment; "setOwner(address)": FunctionFragment; }' is not assignable to type '{ [name: string]: FunctionFragment; }'.
      Property '"createPool(address,address,uint24)"' is incompatible with index signature.
        Type 'import("/home/debo/bangfinals/v3-core/node_modules/@ethersproject/abi/lib/fragments").FunctionFragment' is not assignable to type 'import("/home/debo/bangfinals/v3-core/node_modules/ethers/node_modules/@ethersproject/abi/lib/fragments").FunctionFragment'.
          Types of property 'gas' are incompatible.
            Type 'import("/home/debo/bangfinals/v3-core/node_modules/@ethersproject/bignumber/lib/bignumber").BigNumber | undefined' is not assignable to type 'import("/home/debo/bangfinals/v3-core/node_modules/ethers/node_modules/@ethersproject/bignumber/lib/bignumber").BigNumber | undefined'.
              Type 'import("/home/debo/bangfinals/v3-core/node_modules/@ethersproject/bignumber/lib/bignumber").BigNumber' is not assignable to type 'import("/home/debo/bangfinals/v3-core/node_modules/ethers/node_modules/@ethersproject/bignumber/lib/bignumber").BigNumber'.
                Types of property 'add' are incompatible.
                  Type '(other: import("/home/debo/bangfinals/v3-core/node_modules/@ethersproject/bignumber/lib/bignumber").BigNumberish) => import("/home/debo/bangfinals/v3-core/node_modules/@ethersproject/bignumber/lib/bignumber").BigNumber' is not assignable to type '(other: import("/home/debo/bangfinals/v3-core/node_modules/ethers/node_modules/@ethersproject/bignumber/lib/bignumber").BigNumberish) => import("/home/debo/bangfinals/v3-core/node_modules/ethers/node_modules/@ethersproject/bignumber/lib/bignumber").BigNumber'.
                    Types of parameters 'other' and 'other' are incompatible.
                      Type 'import("/home/debo/bangfinals/v3-core/node_modules/ethers/node_modules/@ethersproject/bignumber/lib/bignumber").BigNumberish' is not assignable to type 'import("/home/debo/bangfinals/v3-core/node_modules/@ethersproject/bignumber/lib/bignumber").BigNumberish'.
                        Type 'BigNumber' is not assignable to type 'BigNumberish'.
                          Property 'toBigInt' is missing in type 'import("/home/debo/bangfinals/v3-core/node_modules/ethers/node_modules/@ethersproject/bignumber/lib/bignumber").BigNumber' but required in type 'import("/home/debo/bangfinals/v3-core/node_modules/@ethersproject/bignumber/lib/bignumber").BigNumber'.

23 interface PanaromaswapV3FactoryInterface extends ethers.utils.Interface {
             ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

  node_modules/@ethersproject/bignumber/lib/bignumber.d.ts:31:5
    31     toBigInt(): bigint;
           ~~~~~~~~
    'toBigInt' is declared here.

````
refer the attachment for the typechainfile. 
[PanaromaswapV3Factory.d.zip](https://github.com/NomicFoundation/hardhat/files/9125626/PanaromaswapV3Factory.d.zip)

This issue is also being [tracked on Linear](https://linear.app/nomic-foundation/issue/HH-967/tserror-тип-unable-to-compile-typescript-[nomicfoundationhardhat2954]).
